Triplets 😂😂 @dhar.mann @imalexstokes We’re giving away 2 new iPhones AND a MacBook 🔥🔥 All you have to do to win is 
1. Tag 2 friends in the comments
2. Follow @dhar.mann @imalexstokes & me

UPDATE! The winners have been DM’d and will be publicly announced this week!!! WINNERS ARE: @rimrock155 / @joyfryend / @piggynicenice CONGRATULATIONS 🎉 

3 winners will be chosen and announced on this post by Friday. 
Best of luck and we can’t wait to send you guys some free stuff! ❤️
